Ask HN: As a researcher, how can I access Similarweb's Ultimate Package API?
text: I reached out to SimialrWeb's sales consultant to get access to their API for my doctoral research. The company said that they do not sell access to their API/Ultimate package for research purposes. The Ultimate Package is only available to enterprises, but it's the only way one can use their API. I'd like to get any advice on how to access, or circumvent to gain access to, SimilarWeb's Ultimate package. Thank you in advance!

Show HN: Layoutit Tokens – edit and export design tokens (supports new DS specs)
text: Layoutit Tokens is a Token Generator that lets you preview, edit, and export tokens for Design System. We currently support the new JSON specs that W3C and the DCTG are working on (no official name yet), also CSS, SASS, DSP and Theo from Salesforce. Free to use and made with open source!
